# Enforce LF line endings for the entire project, on every platform, regardless
# of a checkout's core.autocrlf/core.eol. `text=auto eol=lf` normalizes all text
# files to LF in the repo AND checks them out as LF in the working tree — so a
# Windows clone never rewrites anything to CRLF. This keeps builds, the esbuild
# HUD bundle (overlay/frontend/app.js), and the CI drift-check byte-stable across
# Windows/Linux.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary files: never touch line endings.
*.png binary
*.ico binary
*.exe binary
